                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Các tác giả: Roshan Sharma, Suyoun Kim, Daniel Lazar, Trang Le, Akshat Shrivastava, Kwanghoon Ahn, Piyush Kansal, Leda Sari, Ozlem Kalinli, Michael Seltzer"
